item.title: Mobile Robot I/O Project
item.description: This website document the progress of the Mobile Robot Project, both the discovery of available technologies pertinant to building and afforable mobile vehicle, the engineering process necessary to develop an industrial strength device. And of course, our own implementation of said Robot.
